pe's Initiative to Control Technological Waste</A><DIV CLASS="IndexTS">The European Union (EU) member states are taking action and holding manufacturers responsible for the hazardous materials in their products.</DIV><li class="ITSLI"><A HREF="/yogi/environmental/medicalwaste.html">Treatment of Biohazardous Waste</A><DIV CLASS="IndexTS">Gives insight as to how medical waste is disposed of in America.</DIV><li class="ITSLI"><A HREF="/yogi/environmental/wastehistory.html">The History of Waste</A><DIV CLASS="IndexTS">Do you want to be a Garbologist?</DIV></ul></ul>
